EN: They grilled meat on the beach.
ZH: 我很喜欢吃烤肉串。
EN: I love eating grilled skewers.
ZH: 邻居家正在烤烤肉，闻起来好香。
EN: The neighbors are grilling meat, it smells so good.
ZH: 烧烤的味道使人垂涎三尺。
EN: The smell of barbecue makes people salivate.
