EN: He likes to grill meat outdoors.
ZH: 烤炉被点燃，准备好烤烤肉了。
EN: The grill is lit, ready to cook some barbecue.
ZH: 他每个周末都会在后院烧烤。
EN: He grills in the backyard every weekend.
ZH: 跟朋友一起吃烧烤是一种快乐。
EN: Eating barbecue with friends is a joy.
